# Folder Structure Restructuring Plan

## Problem Statement

The current codebase has **84 flat page files** dumped into a single `/pages` directory, **36 mixed components** with no categorization, hardcoded mock data scattered inside production contexts, no separation between features, and inconsistent patterns. This makes it nearly impossible to onboard developers, track ownership, or scale features independently.

---

## Current Structure (What's Wrong)

```
apps/web/src/
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ pages/              в†ђ 84 files FLAT. SuperAdmin, Student, Counsellor all mixed together
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ Login.tsx
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ CollegeFinder.tsx
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ SuperAdminNewPost.tsx
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ ConsultantDashboard.tsx
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ Accommodation.tsx    в†ђ 60KB single file with hardcoded data
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ CountryDetails.tsx   в†ђ 50KB single file
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ ... (84 files)
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ components/         в†ђ 36 files mixed: modals, sections, layout, navigation
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ context/            в†ђ Auth + Profile + SavedItems + Notifications (mock data inside)
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ services/           в†ђ 4 API services with hardcoded localhost URLs
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ layouts/            в†ђ 4 layouts (good, but scattered)
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ data/               в†ђ Mock data files
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ hooks/              в†ђ 2 hooks
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ shared/             в†ђ 1 nested context
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ features/           в†ђ 1 empty-ish folder
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ types/              в†ђ 1 type declaration
в””в”Ђв”Ђ utils/              в†ђ 1 utility
```

### Core Issues By Perspective

| Perspective | Problem |
|---|---|
| **Product Manager** | Cannot tell which features are real vs mock. No feature ownership boundaries. No way to hand off "the visa module" to a developer. |
| **UI/UX Designer** | No design system. Components mix business logic with presentation. No reusable UI primitives. CSS scattered (some in `.css` files, most in Tailwind inline). |
| **Senior Engineer** | 84 flat files = zero discoverability. Mock data pollutes production contexts. No barrel exports. No feature isolation for testing. API URLs hardcoded across 4 different files. |
| **Security** | Secrets in contexts. No input validation layer. Auth state mixed with UI state. No centralized API client with interceptors for token refresh. |
| **Performance** | No code splitting вЂ” every page imported eagerly in App.tsx. 60KB component files. No lazy loading. |

---

## Proposed Structure

