в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ public.routes.tsx         в†ђ Landing, About, Terms, Countries, Blogs
в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ auth.routes.tsx           в†ђ Login, Signup, ForgotPassword, Verification
в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ student.routes.tsx        в†ђ Dashboard, Feed, Colleges, Profile, etc.
в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ counsellor.routes.tsx     в†ђ Counsellor dashboard, schedule, tasks
в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ superadmin.routes.tsx     в†ђ Admin panel routes
